                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/2014: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Geneva</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gilbert</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-10-09T14:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 9, 1931—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>70. Your 163, October 8, 9 a.m.,<note n="13" xml:id="d153fn13">Not
                        printed.</note> Inform Drummond that I trust that he intends to advise
                    calling the meeting of the Council.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
